RELEVANCE TO SPATIALCVM:
This paper is highly relevant to our Theorem 3 (Multivariate Extension) which
deals with:
1. Copula structures and Sklar's theorem
2. Multivariate empirical processes
3. Weak convergence on function spaces
4. Delta method for dependent data

